          "description": "Don\u2019t cone here unless you want your HIPPA Protected Health Information released for the whole world to see! I\u2019ve been a client for over 13 years and they were releasing legally protected information  illegally without my consent to outside entities the entire time!\n\nDoctors and all health professionals swear an oath to do \u201cno harm.\u201d One Medical is liable for causing me and my family much more harm than good!\n\n***Updates to follow***",
