          "description": "The most relaxing medical appointment you can imagine. Welcoming staff greets you, no redundant paperwork that nobody reads, comfortable waiting area. Unrushed appointment where the doctor does your intake and vitals. Everything ran on time and we finished ahead of schedule. There was even time for her to explain and expand on my questions.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tkUWF6SjNTakU1WlhBMlZYSjJaMVp3TW5GZk0yYxAB!2m1!1s0x0:0x3050bf161bd382cb!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOkdQazJ3SjE5ZXA2VXJ2Z1ZwMnFfM2c%7C%7C?hl=en",
