        {
          "username": "Nick C",
          "rating": 5,
          "contributor_id": "116023182071542814022",
          "user_review_count": 4,
          "user_photo_count": 0,
          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXmtIT1jIR328fx_51WZpQpQlu-U8M-lxGRZxI-hYPo61nj60Yt=s120-c-rp-mo-br100",
          "description": "This was my second time seeing Dr. Courtney Jones at One Medical and every visit has been excellent. From the moment he walks into the room he makes you feel comfortable and truly listened to. He asks thoughtful questions, explains things clearly without rushing, and takes the time to make sure everything is understood. His bedside manner is warm, approachable, and professional, which immediately builds trust.\n\nI appreciate how attentive and thorough he is, not just treating the immediate concern but also looking at the bigger picture of overall health. It is rare to find a doctor who combines medical expertise with genuine care and empathy, and Dr. Jones does both effortlessly.\n\nI always leave my appointments feeling confident in the plan we discuss and grateful to have found such a dedicated physician. I highly recommend Dr. Jones and the One Medical team to anyone looking for excellent, patient centered care.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2sxV2QwZ3dWMHBuTVdWclkyMTNWSHBsYjJSc09FRRAB!2m1!1s0x0:0x3050bf161bd382cb!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOk1Wd0gwV0pnMWVrY213VHplb2RsOEE%7C%7C?hl=en",
